track.name: Catfish Blues
comments: Well I wish... IiIiIiIiiii was a catfish

What a time for music, specifically the marriage of blues and rock.  Hendrix ushered in a whole new way to play guitar.  And  Mitchell on drums!!! Move over John Bonham, Mitch Mitchell had it all over you.
He sure could the blues all right......there won't be anyone like Jimi again.

Although he was rooted in the Blues, he was able to fly in the sky.
